{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"173097-vaca-com-um-so-chifre","title":"Vaca Com Um Só Chifre","description":"Find out about an unique cow.","language":"Portuguese","langCode":"pt","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Nadia Morais","Translators withoutBorders"],"illustrators":["Marion  Drew"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"African Storybook Initiative","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/173097-vaca-com-um-so-chifre"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/237006/size3/81f371d8ed4a11267f72f3cecf65d277.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/237006/size6/81f371d8ed4a11267f72f3cecf65d277.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/228034/size6/188412874d8261d374230a92f6c76174.jpg","text":"Lá em casa, temos uma vaca linda!","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/228035/size6/6ebab7fe2953c8087fa37492aa84500f.jpg","text":"Não tem cauda e só tem um chifre. É tão bonita!","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/228036/size6/0a0f5c818183af2861e355f4a1008901.jpg","text":"É gorda e tem uma barriga grande.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/228037/size6/591921dfc503cbb19de12d6b4ffe51e5.jpg","text":"É a vaca mais forte de todas.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/228038/size6/5b7b2ac4c103afc2fcca04a793f69ccf.jpg","text":"O pastor adora a vaca. Ensinou-a a ouvir apenas a sua voz.","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/228039/size6/2e5bb2e6f1ccce0b77c1120d8fbcb68b.jpg","text":"Quando a manada vai para os campos pastar, esta vaca fica a comer sozinha.","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/228040/size6/095bd550766491e99e9cfa6e3243c03e.jpg","text":"Esta vaca é uma grande lutadora, por isso, as outras deixam-na em paz.","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/228041/size6/fb8da635831e326afdb4c447bde6c595.jpg","text":"As pessoas conhecem esta vaca. Têm medo dela, porque consegue lutar com o seu chifre. Se conhecesses uma vaca assim, o que farias?","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":8,"words":94}}